47
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,280
Well, remember.

48
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:05,030
We've worked out who our customer segment is that we're going to target.

49
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:10,180
We've worked out what the positioning is and the value proposition of our brand

50
00:03:10,180 --> 00:03:13,280
and how we're going to differ from our competitors.

51
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:17,030
We've already laid out our channel choices and our pricing.

52
00:03:17,030 --> 00:03:20,890
And so now we're going to pull it together with how we communicate that.

