00:03:20,890 --> 00:03:25,471
And we're going to get back to some fairly fundamental consumer psychology

54
00:03:25,471 --> 00:03:25,970
here.

55
00:03:25,970 --> 00:03:31,610
And there is a well-established model that you may be familiar with.

56
00:03:31,610 --> 00:03:34,570
And it simply goes by the short form of AIDA.

57
00:03:34,570 --> 00:03:36,850
And so what are we dealing with here?

58
00:03:36,850 --> 00:03:41,150
We're dealing with, at the top, awareness.

59
00:03:41,150 --> 00:03:45,960
So is the customer, the potential customer here,

60
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:49,640
is the customer aware of our brand?

61
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,870
They may be already buying in the category.

62
00:03:51,870 --> 00:03:53,660
But are they aware that we exist?

63
00:03:53,660 --> 00:03:57,630
So this is a kind of a yes or no type decision.

64
00:03:57,630 --> 00:04:02,000
And so we have to use marketing communication tools there.

65
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:05,710
The next is, have we generated within them

66
00:04:05,710 --> 00:04:09,120
an interest for our brand to solve a particular problem

67
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,970
or need that they have?

68
00:04:10,970 --> 00:04:15,750
Then, have they gone from a general interest to a desire or a preference?

69
00:04:15,750 --> 00:04:17,890
This is a prepurchase state.

70
00:04:17,890 --> 00:04:21,410
And then finally, have we prompted an action

71
00:04:21,410 --> 00:04:25,720
which typically is trial or purchase?

72
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:28,900
And then we'd also be interested in what happens

73
00:04:28,900 --> 00:04:30,680
in their post-purchase behavior.

74
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:34,160
Do they retain and re-buy, et cetera, et cetera?

75
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:37,360
But we'll stay with these four elements for now

76
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:40,640
because the marketing communication objectives

77
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:43,040
will vary depending on where our customer

78
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:46,560
segment is in this particular model.

79
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:52,100
And then we will make choices about what combinations of marketing communication

